@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jfkocr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    v2 = (tmp / v0)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.91 / v0 + 0.11)) - 0.69)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.44))
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.61) + (tmp + 0.19 * v1 + 0.70)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v1) * wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.57)))
    data[tid] = v0
